Package: inequantiles
Title: Quantile-Based Inequality Indicators for Complex Survey Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Silvia", "Scarpa", , "silvia.scarpa@unimore.it", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4003-1621"))
Description: Provides functions for estimating quantile-based inequality 
    indicators such as the quantile ratio index, quintile share ratio, Palma index
    and quantiles or ratio of them from  complex sampling data. Influence function estimators and
    estimator of the sampling variance via rescaled bootstrap are also provided.
